<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">typing</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">List</span>

<span class="n">TOTAL_VERTICES</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">adjacency_list</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">TOTAL_NODES</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">unique_columns</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">PathFinder</span><span class="p">():</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="fm">__init__</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">adjacency_matrix</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">List</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">List</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">]])</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="kc">None</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">adjacency_matrix</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">adjacency_matrix</span>
        

    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">all_paths_helper</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">city_name_from</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nb">str</span> <span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">city_name_to</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">visited</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">List</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="nb">bool</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">path</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">List</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">all_paths</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">List</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">List</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">]])</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">city_name_from_index</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">unique_columns</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">index</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">city_name_from</span><span class="p">)</span>

        <span class="n">visited</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">city_name_from_index</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="kc">True</span>
        <span class="n">path</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">city_name_from</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">city_name_from</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="n">city_name_to</span> <span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">all_paths</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">path</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">copy</span><span class="p">())</span>
<span class="c1">#             print(path)</span>
        <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">neighbours</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">adjacency_matrix</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">city_name_from_index</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">city_name_from_index</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">index</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">neighbours</span><span class="p">)):</span>
                <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">neighbours</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">index</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">:</span>
                    <span class="n">neighbour</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">unique_columns</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">index</span><span class="p">]</span>
                    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">visited</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">index</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="kc">False</span><span class="p">:</span>
                        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">all_paths_helper</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">neighbour</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">city_name_to</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">visited</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">path</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">all_paths</span><span class="p">)</span>

        <span class="c1">#for all neighbours of this path call ourselbes</span>
        <span class="n">path</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pop</span><span class="p">()</span> 
        <span class="n">visited</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">city_name_from_index</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="kc">False</span>
        

    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">all_paths</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">city_name_from</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nb">str</span> <span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">city_name_to</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="ow">not</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">city_name_from</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">unique_columns</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="n">city_name_to</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">unique_columns</span><span class="p">):</span>
            <span class="k">return</span> <span class="s2">&quot;Incorrect City&quot;</span>

        <span class="n">visited</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="kc">False</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">TOTAL_NODES</span>
        <span class="n">path</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
        <span class="n">all_paths</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">all_paths_helper</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">city_name_from</span> <span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">city_name_to</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">visited</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">path</span> <span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">all_paths</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">all_paths</span>



<span class="n">pf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">PathFinder</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">adjacency_matrix</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">all_paths</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pf</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">all_paths</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;DARWIN&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">&quot;SYDNEY&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
